ot indeed. Mobster aimed Grenade's flamethrower, and managed to destroy the=
 ice ball with it. Then the fireballs came. Mobster tried to switch to Krac=
ken's ice gun, but too late, bang! Mobster slaps at himself to put the fire=
 out. It does in fact, though, start to defrost his arm. Was he working on =
Gigas' brain? He must have been! He fired the flamethrower at his arm and m=
elted the ice. He took the gun back in his left arm. Horn Drill had been kn=
own to be perfect at almost everything. Mobster aimed at Necromancer's head=
, and fired...
